課程概述 Course Description
       一、教學目標：本課程將以跨領域與開放性方法探索音樂藝術研究的脈絡，包含文化背景和音樂功能，期望學生從中瞭解系統音樂學的特殊性，確立音樂學的基礎知識與基礎研究能力。二、教學內容：系統音樂學是以音樂歷史學及民族音樂學為先導，所發展出來的一門學科。基於多元文化與價值相對的觀念，不同學術背景的音樂學者，重新思考審視研究的對象與研究的方法。課程內容包含各音樂理論、種不同音樂樣式的法則及音樂的文化意義。討論主題集中於「律學」、「音樂與文化認同」、「音樂與社會」以及「音樂與演出」等。三、教學進度：（一）課程說明、音樂藝術的本質（二）工具書與基礎書目之學習（三）論文格式與報告之撰寫（四）音樂學研究法則與基本訓練（五）介紹四大系統音樂學（六）音樂歷史學的特質（七）民族音樂學的質性（八）解析音樂的體裁：音樂要素介紹（九）音樂句法的詮釋、樂曲類型及其功能（十）不同的音樂風格Course Objectives --The course will explore Systematic Musicology in respect to the cultural background, and music’s functionality through interdisciplinary and open-minded explorations according to music research of the choroid, learning the basics of musicology and basic research capabilities. Course Description--Systematic Musicology use of Music History and Ethno- musicology as a model, because of Musicology specificity, scholars of different fields re-examine the object of study and research method.  The courses contents include the basic concept of music theory, different music styles, as well as the analysis of the music’s cultural significance. Included are "Study of Temperament", "Music and Cultural Identity", "Music and Society", as well as "Music and Performance" and so on. Course Schedule--1. About the Course; the Essence of Music. 2. Bibliography of Books and Basic Tools for Learning. 3. Paper Format and Report Writing. 4. Music Studies Rule and Basic Training. 5. Four Main Systems of the Musicology. 6. According to Historical Evolution, Construct the Musicology. 7.According to Ethnomusicological Quality, Construct the Musicology8.Music Texture: Introduction to the Various Elements of Music. 9.Annotation of Music Structures; General Music, Song, Dance Music, Festival. 10.Music and its Function, etc. 11.Introduction to the Various Music Styles    

課程學習目標 Course Objectives    
	    一、教學目標 Course Objectives
　　本課程將以跨領域與開放性方法探索音樂藝術研究的脈絡，包含文化背景和音樂功能，期望學生從中瞭解系統音樂學的特殊性，確立音樂學的基礎知識與基礎研究能力。
The course will explore Systematic Musicology in respect to the cultural background, and music’s functionality through interdisciplinary and open-minded explorations according to music research of the choroid, learning the basics of musicology and basic research capabilities.
 
二、教學內容 Course Description
　　系統音樂學是以音樂歷史學及民族音樂學為先導，所發展出來的一門學科。基於多元文化與價值相對的觀念，不同學術背景的音樂學者，重新思考審視研究的對象與研究的方法。課程內容包含各音樂理論、種不同音樂樣式的法則及音樂的文化意義。討論主題集中於「律學」、「音樂與文化認同」、「音樂與社會」以及「音樂與演出」等。
Systematic Musicology use of Music History and Ethno- musicology as a model, because of Musicology specificity, scholars of different fields re-examine the object of study and research method.  The courses contents include the basic concept of music theory, different music styles, as well as the analysis of the music’s cultural significance. Included are "Study of Temperament", "Music and Cultural Identity", "Music and Society", as well as "Music and Performance" and so on.
     

課程進度 Course Outline


週次 Week進度說明 Progress Description
1課程說明、音樂藝術的本質2課程說明、音樂藝術的本質3工具書與基礎書目之學習4論文格式與報告之撰寫5音樂學研究法則與基本訓練6音樂學研究法則與基本訓練7介紹四大系統音樂學8介紹四大系統音樂學9音樂歷史學的特質10音樂歷史學的特質11民族音樂學的質性12民族音樂學的質性13解析音樂的體裁：音樂要素介紹14解析音樂的體裁：音樂要素介紹15音樂句法的詮釋、樂曲類型及其功能16音樂句法的詮釋、樂曲類型及其功能17不同的音樂風格18不同的音樂風格 

